HEADWORD: Pamphleteer
<hw>Pam`phlet*eer"</hw> <pr>(p⟦acr⟧m`fl⟦ecr⟧t*⟦emac⟧r")</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <def>A writer of pamphlets; a scribbler.</def>
