==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Pamphleteer
<hw>Pam`phlet*eer"</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To write or publish
pamphlets.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>By <qex>pamphleteering</qex> we shall not win.</q> <rj><qau>C.
Kingsley.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

